---
import config from '../../site.json';
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="fade-in-up">
        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-3xl aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden border border-base-300/50">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441986300917-64674bd600d8?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Our story" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <span class="badge badge-outline border-accent text-accent text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">Built for the<br /><span class="text-accent">Culture</span></h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We started with a simple idea: create a space where creativity meets commerce. Every product in our store represents the work of artists, designers, and makers who pour their soul into what they create.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          This isn't just a store — it's a platform for the culture. From handcrafted goods to limited-edition drops, everything here tells a story.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-accent">500+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/50">Products</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-accent">50+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/50">Creators</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-accent">10K+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/50">Customers</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
